14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_PTR_12_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_PTR_12_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_PTR_ATTRIBUTES (0)
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_ptr(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(rdclass);
29 UNUSED(callbacks);
30
31 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
32 false));
33
34 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
35 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
36 if (origin == NULL)
37 origin = dns_rootname;
38 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
39 if (rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in &&
40 (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0 &&
41 (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKREVERSE) != 0) {
42 bool ok;
43 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
44 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
45 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
46 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
47 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
48 }
49 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
50}
51
52static inline isc_result_t
53totext_ptr(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
54 isc_region_t region;
55 dns_name_t name;
56 dns_name_t prefix;
57 bool sub;
58
59 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
60 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
61
62 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
63 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
64
65 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
66 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
67
68 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
69
70 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
71}
72
73static inline isc_result_t
74fromwire_ptr(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
75 dns_name_t name;
76
77 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
78
79 UNUSED(type);
80 UNUSED(rdclass);
81
82 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
83
84 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
85 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
86}
87
88static inline isc_result_t
89towire_ptr(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
90 dns_name_t name;
91 dns_offsets_t offsets;
92 isc_region_t region;
93
94 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
95 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
96
97 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
98
99 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
100 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
101 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
102
103 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
104}
105
106static inline int
107compare_ptr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
108 dns_name_t name1;
109 dns_name_t name2;
110 isc_region_t region1;
111 isc_region_t region2;
112
113 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
115 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
116 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
117 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
118
119 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
120 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
121
122 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
123 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
124
125 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
126 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
127
128 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
129}
130
131static inline isc_result_t
132fromstruct_ptr(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
133 dns_rdata_ptr_t *ptr = source;
134 isc_region_t region;
135
136 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
137 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
138 REQUIRE(ptr->common.rdtype == type);
139 REQUIRE(ptr->common.rdclass == rdclass);
140
141 UNUSED(type);
142 UNUSED(rdclass);
143
144 dns_name_toregion(&ptr->ptr, &region);
145 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
146}
147
148static inline isc_result_t
149tostruct_ptr(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
150 isc_region_t region;
151 dns_rdata_ptr_t *ptr = target;
152 dns_name_t name;
153
154 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
155 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
156 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
157
158 ptr->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
159 ptr->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
160 ISC_LINK_INIT(&ptr->common, link);
161
162 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
163 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
164 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
165 dns_name_init(&ptr->ptr, NULL);
166 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &ptr->ptr));
167 ptr->mctx = mctx;
168 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
169}
170
171static inline void
172freestruct_ptr(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
173 dns_rdata_ptr_t *ptr = source;
174
175 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
176 REQUIRE(ptr->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
177
178 if (ptr->mctx == NULL)
179 return;
180
181 dns_name_free(&ptr->ptr, ptr->mctx);
182 ptr->mctx = NULL;
183}
184
185static inline isc_result_t
186additionaldata_ptr(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
187 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
188
189 UNUSED(rdata);
190 UNUSED(add);
191 UNUSED(arg);
192
193 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
194}
195
196static inline isc_result_t
197digest_ptr(ARGS_DIGEST) {
198 isc_region_t r;
199 dns_name_t name;
200
201 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
202
203 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
204 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
205 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
206
207 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
208}

210static inline bool
211checkowner_ptr(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
212
213 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
214
215 UNUSED(name);
216 UNUSED(type);
217 UNUSED(rdclass);
218 UNUSED(wildcard);
219
220 return (true);
221}

223static unsigned char ip6_arpa_data[] = "\003IP6\004ARPA";
224static unsigned char ip6_arpa_offsets[] = { 0, 4, 9 };
225static const dns_name_t ip6_arpa =
226 DNS_NAME_INITABSOLUTE(ip6_arpa_data, ip6_arpa_offsets);
227
228static unsigned char ip6_int_data[] = "\003IP6\003INT";
229static unsigned char ip6_int_offsets[] = { 0, 4, 8 };
230static const dns_name_t ip6_int =
231 DNS_NAME_INITABSOLUTE(ip6_int_data, ip6_int_offsets);
232
233static unsigned char in_addr_arpa_data[] = "\007IN-ADDR\004ARPA";
234static unsigned char in_addr_arpa_offsets[] = { 0, 8, 13 };
235static const dns_name_t in_addr_arpa =
236 DNS_NAME_INITABSOLUTE(in_addr_arpa_data, in_addr_arpa_offsets);
237
238static inline bool
239checknames_ptr(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
240 isc_region_t region;
241 dns_name_t name;
242
243 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_ptr);
244
245 if (rdata->rdclass != dns_rdataclass_in)
246 return (true);
247
248 if (dns_name_isdnssd(owner))
249 return (true);
250
251 if (dns_name_issubdomain(owner, &in_addr_arpa) ||
252 dns_name_issubdomain(owner, &ip6_arpa) ||
253 dns_name_issubdomain(owner, &ip6_int)) {
254 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
255 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
256 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
257 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
258 if (bad != NULL)
259 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
260 return (false);
261 }
262 }
263 return (true);
264}
265
266static inline int
267casecompare_ptr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
268 return (compare_ptr(rdata1, rdata2));
269}
